# Define the construct mapping:\
# Dignity-Self:  Q5-Q10,   correct answer = 1\
# Dignity-Other: Q11-Q16,  correct answer = 2\
# Honor-Self:    Q17-Q22,  correct answer = 3\
# Honor-Other:   Q23-Q29,  correct answer = 4\
# Face-Self:     Q30-Q35,  correct answer = 5\
# Face-Other:    Q36-Q40,  correct answer = 6\
\
